column2: Johnny Depp will always, and always will be Captain Jack Sparrow 100%❤
column44: Johnny Depp is the ONLY Jack Sparrow
column51: Johnny Depp is the ONLY Jack Sparrow
column52:
Sign this if you agree that Jack Sparrow should not be casted as someone else. Sign this if you support Jonny Depp as an actor and believe his career should not be concerned with his personal affairs. Regardless of who did what to who. The movie needs Johnny. 

You may have heard that there are some drama’s going on with Johnny Depp and Amber. Disney has decided because of his personal life that they are casting someone else as Captain Jack Sparrow for the future Pirates of the Caribbean movies. If you have seen the movies at all, he is rightfully the star and this idea is absurd especially because his personal affairs should have nothing to do with his carrier, regardless if allegations are true or not. 

I am signing this partition not only to stand up for Johnny’s rights but for the sake of the movies which recasting is always a bad decision. If you have ever been fired from a job because of something that happened at home, you might understand how unfair and unjust such an event is.

Let’s stand up for Johnny and Sparrow!
